(193, 1, '2018-05-09 11:18:08', '2018-05-09 11:18:08', '{\n    \"zerif-lite-child::zerif_aboutus_biglefttitle\": {\n        \"value\": \"REFINED WITH EXPERIENCE\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2018-05-09 11:11:04\"\n    },\n    \"zerif-lite-child::zerif_aboutus_text\": {\n        \"value\": \"Since highschool I am already exposed with HTML Codes. It started with curiosity. My classmate have a book with lot\'s of HTML codes. Everyday we are studying it until we manage to adopt some of it.\\n\\nYear 2013 I started working with Web Development. I started with Pure HTML and CSS development. Later on, as our company doesn\'t have enough employee, they decided to put me thru the test of working with CMS specifically Wordpress. As the time goes by, I manage to adopt with CMS\'s. I already tried working with Wordpress, Joomla and Magento. After 6 months of hard work and smart working, I become a Team Leader of our Web Development Team on my first company. \\n\\nThat\'s how my Web Dev Life starts.\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2018-05-09 11:11:04\"\n    },\n    \"widget_ctup-ads-widget[1]\": {\n        \"value\": {\n            \"encoded_serialized_instance\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"GAMER\",\n            \"is_widget_customizer_js_value\": true,\n            \"instance_hash_key\": \"c425f60ac5a38b7cadc80701f497c3d8\"\n        },\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2018-05-09 11:12:04\"\n    },\n    \"widget_ctup-ads-widget[2]\": {\n        \"value\": {\n            \"encoded_serialized_instance\": \"\",\n            \"title\": \"MUSICIAN\",\n            \"is_widget_customizer_js_value\": true,\n            \"instance_hash_key\": \"56678e0462488c09de78ff4fa87c0708\"\n        },\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2018-05-09 11:12:04\"